text.text: This place is very sacred place. In Ramayan time Prabhu Shri Ram, Sita and Laxman pass through this place. There is an ancient reservoir Kund here. which is called Ram Kund. There are many temples inside this place. Here the saints who do the Narmada Parikrama mostly come here to stay. There is a good arrangement for food etc. for the devotees, Also this place contains śmaśāna (श्मशान) is a Hindu crematory ground, where dead bodies are brought to be burnt on a pyre.
